valid_queries.sql: SELECT AVG("regular_season_detailed_results"."wto" + "regular_season_detailed_results"."lfta") as agg_0 FROM "tourney_slots" LEFT OUTER JOIN "seasons" ON "tourney_slots"."season" = "seasons"."season" LEFT OUTER JOIN "regular_season_detailed_results" ON "seasons"."season" = "regular_season_detailed_results"."season" LEFT OUTER JOIN "teams" ON "regular_season_detailed_results"."wteam" = "teams"."team_id"  WHERE "teams"."team_id" <= 1382

descriptor.table: tournament:Query[SELECT "season_0", "wteam_1", "wto_2", "lfta_3", "team_id_4" FROM (SELECT "season" AS "season_0", "wteam" AS "wteam_1", "wto" AS "wto_2", "lfta" AS "lfta_3" FROM (SELECT "season", "wteam", "wto", "lfta" FROM "public"."regular_season_detailed_results" WHERE "wteam" <= ?) l) l INNER JOIN (SELECT "team_id" AS "team_id_4" FROM (SELECT "team_id" FROM "public"."teams" WHERE "team_id" <= ?) r) r ON (("wteam_1") = ("team_id_4"))] columns=[season_0:integer:int4, wto_2:integer:int4, lfta_3:integer:int4]

tournament:Query[SELECT "season_0", "season_1" FROM (SELECT "season" AS "season_0" FROM (SELECT "season" FROM "public"."tourney_slots") l) l LEFT JOIN (SELECT "season" AS "season_1" FROM (SELECT "season" FROM "public"."seasons") r) r ON (("season_0") = ("season_1"))] columns=[season_1:integer:int4]

valid_queries.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, SUM("tourney_slots"."season") as agg_1 FROM "tourney_slots"  WHERE "tourney_slots"."slot" = 'R1Z7' AND "tourney_slots"."season" != 2009 AND "tourney_slots"."weakseed" = 'Z10' AND "tourney_slots"."strongseed" = 'R1X4'

descriptor.table: tournament:Query[SELECT count(*) AS "_pfgnrtd_1", sum("_pfgnrtd_0") AS "_pfgnrtd_2" FROM (SELECT CAST("season" AS bigint) AS "_pfgnrtd_0" FROM "public"."tourney_slots" WHERE "strongseed" = ? AND "slot" = ? AND NOT ("season" = ?) AND "weakseed" = ?) o] columns=[_pfgnrtd_1:bigint:bigint, _pfgnrtd_2:bigint:bigint]

valid_queries.sql: SELECT AVG("target"."pred" + "tourney_detailed_results"."season") as agg_0, AVG("tourney_seeds"."season") as agg_1, SUM("tourney_detailed_results"."numot" + "tourney_detailed_results"."lfgm3") as agg_2 FROM "target" LEFT OUTER JOIN "teams" ON "target"."team_id1" = "teams"."team_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "tourney_compact_results" ON "teams"."team_id" = "tourney_compact_results"."wteam" LEFT OUTER JOIN "tourney_detailed_results" ON "teams"."team_id" = "tourney_detailed_results"."wteam" LEFT OUTER JOIN "tourney_seeds" ON "teams"."team_id" = "tourney_seeds"."team"  WHERE "target"."team_id1_wins" >= 0

descriptor.table: tournament:Query[SELECT "team_id1_0", "pred_1", "team_id_2" FROM (SELECT "team_id1" AS "team_id1_0", "pred" AS "pred_1" FROM (SELECT "team_id1", "pred" FROM "public"."target" WHERE "team_id1_wins" >= ?) l) l LEFT JOIN (SELECT "team_id" AS "team_id_2" FROM (SELECT "team_id" FROM "public"."teams") r) r ON (("team_id1_0") = ("team_id_2"))] columns=[pred_1:double:float8, team_id_2:integer:int4]
tournament:public.tourney_compact_results public.tourney_compact_results columns=[wteam:integer:int4]
tournament:public.tourney_detailed_results public.tourney_detailed_results columns=[season:integer:int4, wteam:integer:int4, numot:integer:int4, lfgm3:integer:int4]
tournament:public.tourney_seeds public.tourney_seeds columns=[season:integer:int4, team:integer:int4]

valid_queries.sql: SELECT AVG("tourney_compact_results"."lteam") as agg_0, AVG("tourney_detailed_results"."wblk" + "tourney_detailed_results"."lfgm") as agg_1 FROM "teams" LEFT OUTER JOIN "tourney_detailed_results" ON "teams"."team_id" = "tourney_detailed_results"."wteam" LEFT OUTER JOIN "tourney_compact_results" ON "teams"."team_id" = "tourney_compact_results"."wteam"  WHERE "tourney_detailed_results"."lfga3" != 19 AND "tourney_compact_results"."wteam" <= 1266 AND "tourney_detailed_results"."wfta" != 21 AND "teams"."team_id" >= 1383
SELECT SUM("tourney_slots"."season") as agg_0, AVG("tourney_slots"."season") as agg_1, SUM("tourney_slots"."season") as agg_2 FROM "tourney_slots"  WHERE "tourney_slots"."weakseed" != 'Y09'

descriptor.table: tournament:public.tourney_slots public.tourney_slots columns=[season:integer:int4, weakseed:varchar(255):varchar]

valid_queries.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, SUM("regular_season_detailed_results"."lfga3" + "regular_season_detailed_results"."wfga3") as agg_1, SUM("regular_season_detailed_results"."wor" + "regular_season_detailed_results"."wftm") as agg_2 FROM "teams" LEFT OUTER JOIN "regular_season_detailed_results" ON "teams"."team_id" = "regular_season_detailed_results"."wteam" LEFT OUTER JOIN "tourney_compact_results" ON "teams"."team_id" = "tourney_compact_results"."wteam" LEFT OUTER JOIN "target" ON "teams"."team_id" = "target"."team_id1"  WHERE "tourney_compact_results"."season" <= 2008

descriptor.table: tournament:Query[SELECT "wteam_0", "wfga3_1", "wftm_2", "wor_3", "lfga3_4", "team_id_5" FROM (SELECT "wteam" AS "wteam_0", "wfga3" AS "wfga3_1", "wftm" AS "wftm_2", "wor" AS "wor_3", "lfga3" AS "lfga3_4" FROM (SELECT "wteam", "wfga3", "wftm", "wor", "lfga3" FROM "public"."regular_season_detailed_results") l) l RIGHT JOIN (SELECT "team_id" AS "team_id_5" FROM (SELECT "team_id" FROM "public"."teams") r) r ON (("wteam_0") = ("team_id_5"))] columns=[lfga3_4:integer:int4, wftm_2:integer:int4, wfga3_1:integer:int4, wor_3:integer:int4, team_id_5:integer:int4]
tournament:public.tourney_compact_results public.tourney_compact_results constraint on [season] columns=[wteam:integer:int4]
tournament:public.target public.target columns=[team_id1:integer:int4]

valid_queries.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, SUM("tourney_detailed_results"."lpf" + "regular_season_detailed_results"."lfta") as agg_1, SUM("tourney_detailed_results"."lor" + "tourney_detailed_results"."wor") as agg_2 FROM "tourney_seeds" LEFT OUTER JOIN "teams" ON "tourney_seeds"."team" = "teams"."team_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "regular_season_detailed_results" ON "teams"."team_id" = "regular_season_detailed_results"."wteam" LEFT OUTER JOIN "tourney_detailed_results" ON "teams"."team_id" = "tourney_detailed_results"."wteam"  WHERE "regular_season_detailed_results"."lfga" != 57 AND "regular_season_detailed_results"."last" = 10 AND "teams"."team_id" <= 1101 AND "teams"."team_name" != 'UNLV' AND "tourney_seeds"."season" >= 2002
